text: Elizabeth Tulloch is an American actress. She acts in movies and television programs. She starred as Jackie in the independent movie Caroline and Jackie. Tulloch also played as Nadine in Lakeview Terrace, a crime movie from 2009. She plays Juliet in Grimm. Tulloch was born in San Diego.
